<plot>A documentary hosted by 'Pierce Brosnan' (qv) examining the facts and legends surrounding the real Robin Hood. Scenes from the 1991 film _Robin Hood: Prince of Thieves (1991)_ (qv)--for which this documentary was intended to be a companion piece--are shown, along with interviews with cast and crew.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?465534</url></doc>
